      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Composition Law Contract\n\nThis contract defines how Twilite should compose multiple nodesets in the same graph without turning structure into ceremony.\n\nIt is a decision surface for when to use domain nodes, template nodes, contract nodes, or plain markdown.",
